				<td colspan="2"><span>Dessicated Halfling Mask
<br />
MAGIC ITEM  LORE ITEM  NO DROP  
<br />
Slot: FACE  
<br />
AC: 4
<br />
CHA: +7  AGI: +7  
<br />
Effect: Illusion: Halfling (Casting Time: 8.0)
<br />
WT:  1.1    Size: SMALL
<br />
Class: BRD ROG ENC 
<br />
Race: ALL
<br />
Slot 1, type 7: empty
<br />

<br />
I'm looking for more masks to add to my collection and am also looking to do it in a place that has exp as well.  At 55 I'm pretty sure Chardok will still be good experience (though it's hard to pull me away from PoD atm).
<br />

<br />
Can anyone tell me how hard this camp is to get to and hold, and lastly how many it would take with moderate levels (55-60).
<br />

<br />
I have heard this camp is long for the mask, but I figure if I can do it while exp is actually involved, it may not be so painfull.</span></td>
