				<td colspan="2"><span>The camp would take some time to get to if you fought your way down with those levels.  If everybody knows the path, you could selos/sow up outside and run to ChardokB to clear aggro and setup base camp there until you can move in.  If not, expect a hour or so to fight down at the least I'd say.
<br />

<br />
Having just got my mask though, if you camp it with a group expect many to not want to live there with you as it can take some time to get.  I went thru quite some time and phs before I finally got mine.
<br />

<br />
But I love it when my guild bitches about my being a halfling all the time now.  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-4.gif" border="0" alt="Tongue out" hspace="2" /></span></td>
